# Trivy ignore file
# Add patterns here to exclude false positives from security scans

# Test files with mock credentials (these are intentional)
**/tests/**
**/test_*.py
**/*_test.py
**/conftest.py

# Example/template files
**/*.example
**/*.example.*
**/example/**

# Documentation
**/docs/**
**/*.md

# Development tools
**/ferramentas/**
**/.venv/**
**/node_modules/**

# Langfuse submodule (external dependency)
langfuse/**
